# DOEoptimizer

**DOEoptimizer** is an R package that provides several optimization algorithms designed to optimize design of physical experiments criteria (matrix input functions). It offers tools and utilities for constructing efficient experimental designs through genetic algorithms, simulated annealing, stochastic optimization, and greedy strategies.

